[   23.302362]  ? snd_cml_rt1011_probe+0x23a/0x3d0 [snd_soc_cml_rt1011_rt5682]
[   23.302365]  __kasan_report.cold+0x37/0x86
[   23.302371]  ? snd_cml_rt1011_probe+0x23a/0x3d0 [snd_soc_cml_rt1011_rt5682]
